Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper deals with natural language processing and relation discovery from text corpus. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper proposes a new approach to improve the state-of-the-art performance in relation discovery. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is relevant as the paper uses a variational auto-encoder based algorithm for relation discovery. 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is relevant as the paper deals with discovering relations from a text corpus. 
- cs.DB (Databases) is relevant as the paper uses knowledge bases to supervise the relation discovery process.
